=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de8bcbda729e1d3ddd2d67850bb0210f31439c7","tid":391013,"uid":89166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊間<br />\n中途有冇後悔咁摺</blockquote><br />\n勉強做d自己唔想做既野唔會開心</blockquote><br />\n有時見中同咁投入唔覺得 自己好似差咁啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾中意摺 但係感覺會錯過一啲重要野"},{"pid":"56b2f97d9fbbcf2601436b6ef74f82df4bb144c6","tid":391013,"uid":35766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"點入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ba3f964810b384026bdc8ec557d9d5649b61ee","tid":391013,"uid":97465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"做少你一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：3年舊制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a0e0c02dd020ed7e8be424115e20c44c991bc3","tid":391013,"uid":55522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"有冇試過yo人先"},{"pid":"16da2d6cdf52e62b8ac2cbb1ca6fd6cbba852719","tid":391013,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:18:15.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"3c728c2629ca0eae2b16ec7b08b071276f255e5d","tid":391013,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:00:28.000Z","msg":"有冇叫雞"},{"pid":"7e2a3b63315d8afd22385df3ecf3593f89b0a042","tid":391013,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊間<br />\n中途有冇後悔咁摺</blockquote><br />\n勉強做d自己唔想做既野唔會開心</blockquote><br />\n有時見中同咁投入唔覺得 自己好似差咁啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾中意摺 但係感覺會錯過一啲重要野</blockquote><br />\n大家性格唔同姐"},{"pid":"76807bb9bd28c600a2fc39d4779d855cb7458f76","tid":391013,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點入大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比心機讀書"},{"pid":"be4a7a13c954b043aa31a744be26b57c9cab3b8f","tid":391013,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過yo人先</blockquote><br />\n有試過睇岩女主動拎contact<br />\n出過一次街"}]}